Available Tools: send_email | compose_draft | send_reply | forward_email
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "to": ["string"], "cc": ["string"], "subject": "string", "body": "string", "attachments": ["string"] }
Response Schema: { "message_id": "string", "status": "sent|draft|failed", "timestamp": "string" }
---
Question: Email the quarterly budget forecast to the finance committee.
Call: { "func_call": "send_email", "to": ["cfo@globalinc.com", "analyst@globalinc.com"], "cc": ["auditor@globalinc.com"], "subject": "Q4 Budget Forecast - Final Draft", "body": "Hi Committee,\n\nPlease review the attached Q4 budget forecast. We need approval by Thursday to proceed with allocations.\n\nRegards,\nSarah Jenkins", "attachments": ["q4_budget_forecast.xlsx"] }
Response: { "message_id": "msg_10293m", "status": "sent", "timestamp": "2023-10-25T09:15:00Z" }

